      • parseScanSat

        public static SatelliteDescription parseScanSat​(java.lang.String line)
                                         throws SSCDatabaseLockedException
        Parses a line of output from the scansat program for a satellite's description.
        Parameters:
        line - a line of output from the scansat program.
        Returns:

        SSCDatabaseLockedException - if a database lock is detected.
